H3.text: What city celebrates the original Oktoberfest. DEMUC

A4.text: It is held annually in Munich on the Theresienwiese from mid-September to the first Sunday in October.

A5.text: The first Oktoberfest was held on 12 October 1810 to celebrate the wedding of Crown Prince Ludwig and Princess Therese of Saxony-Hildburghausen.
